<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦咦？<delay20 />你該不會是
<tag a="110" b="4" />吧？<delay20 /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />沒錯吧！？<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />我們已經<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="90" b="1" arg="0x2" />年沒見了耶～！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說啊，<delay20 /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也真是的～！<delay40 />
放著我們島不管跑去哪裡做什麼啦～？<delay40 />
我超～擔心你的說～！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我寂寞了這麼久，<delay8 />
可是要付出很大的代價喔？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就負起責任陪我大玩特玩吧～！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！？<delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />騙人的吧～！<delay40 /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想～<delay8 />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的耶，<delay20 />我們已經<tag a="90" b="1" arg="0x2" />年又<tag a="90" b="1" arg="0x1" />個月沒見了！！<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />你是不是覺得我記得很清楚？<delay40 />
<anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那是因為我一直在等你的消息呀，<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不要再讓我這麼擔心了啦……<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你這麼有精神真是太好了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這不是<tag a="110" b="4" />嗎～<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />歡迎你<delay8 />回來～！<delay40 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我等你好久了～！！<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前還想說<delay8 />你是不是不會再回到這座島上了，<delay8 />
那時候真的超不安的。<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是只要你回來就好，這樣我就很開心了～<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />放心吧！<delay40 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在依然是
