<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們彼此<delay8 />都要過得開心唷～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你之前什麼都沒跟我說就走了，<delay8 />
不覺得這樣很過分嗎～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你不在的時候，<delay20 /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛好被偶像事務所發掘，<delay8 />
就這樣離開島上該怎麼辦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還好這種事沒發生！<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總而言之，<delay40 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />你能回來這裡，<delay8 />我超開心的！<delay40 />
