	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay8 />
我們超久沒見了耶～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺你給人的印象好像跟以前不太一樣？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸欸，<delay8 />那我看起來怎麼樣呢？<delay20 />
我也改變過自己的造型呢～<10_4 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼？<delay20 />你說我完全沒變？<pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等～<delay8 />你再仔細看看，<delay20 />
像我的指甲造型，<delay8 />還有香水之類的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
應該滿有<delay8 />成熟大人的感覺對吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay20 />沒關係啦！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說拜託你，<delay20 />
之後不要再突然搞失蹤了唷～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超～久不見的說～！<delay20 />你過得還好嗎～？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />一定是
為了精進自己最喜歡的<tag a="135" b="8" arg="0xcd00" />技巧，<delay20 />
所以才去修行的，對吧～？<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />那不是你的興趣嗎？<delay40 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之，<delay20 />瞞著我搞失蹤，<delay8 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是要付出很大的代價唷～！<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之後你一定要<delay20 />
