<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們約好囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還在想最近怎麼都沒看到你呢～<delay20 />
是去旅行了嗎～？<pageBreak /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的，<delay20 />至少先跟我說一聲嘛～！<delay40 />
讓我超～級擔<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />咳咳，<delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是有一點點<delay20 />擔心你啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之，<delay20 />
看你這麼有精神，真是太好了。<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你下次不要再突然消失了唷～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />初次見面～！<delay20 />
我叫<tag a="110" b="10" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />將來的夢想<delay8 /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是成為一名偶像！<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />是說<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經<tag a="90" b="1" arg="0x1" />個月沒來找我說話了耶！<delay40 />
害我以為<delay8 />你是不是已經忘記我了～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay8 />我才想重新自我介紹一次，<delay20 />
這樣<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
就會記得我是誰了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一直好想跟你聊聊天～<delay frames="60" />
