	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />～！<delay40 />
好久不見了，<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你到底跑哪裡去啦～？<10_4 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />你其實沒有離開很久？<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不會吧～<delay20 />
難道<delay8 />只有我不常跟
<tag a="110" b="4" />聊天嗎～？<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可能我們<delay20 />都忙著追逐夢想跟填飽肚子，<delay8 />
所以錯過了也說不定，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我好想跟你多聊聊天喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會盡量空出時間的，<delay20 />
你之後<delay8 />也可以更隨意地
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />找我說話喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的～<delay20 />你明明就在這座島上，<delay8 />
